eports/romanian.html The History of the Romanian Language]\n{{Language histories}}\n{{Romanian language}}\n\n[[Category:History of the Romanian language]]\n[[Category:Indo-European linguistics]]\n", "name_user": "Rosenborg BK Fan", "label": "safe", "comment": "\u2192\u200eBackground:Minor edit", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/History_of_Romanian"}
